<taxonomicName authorityName="Ricarte &amp; Marcos-García &amp; Hancock &amp; Rotheray" authorityYear="2012" box="[309,407,1013,1034]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Quichuana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="78" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="argentea">
<emphasis box="[309,407,1013,1034]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="78">argentea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
’ refers to the silver colour of the body hairs.
</paragraph>
